responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "9FD87B9A49F2E235BFED89AC1D3764B1", "I found a gold discus, yet before I could examine it in greater detail, I was assaulted by the undead. I ran and although I escaped, I dropped the discus somewhere. Help me find it. I\'m sure it is a hint to my goal and your riches.")
